	</div>
	<div>
		<div class="comment_header">
		Comment <a href="#c_1713652877">19</a> by Dan Sorensen
		posted on 5/12/2006 at 10:09 PM
		</div>
		<div class="comment_text"><p>Here's my entry... With more time, it should be a seperate form + CFC.</p><p>&lt;!---<br>Title:       Return HTML Comments<br>Author:      Dan Sorensen<br>Date:        May 12, 2006<br>Comment:     Based on the May 12 Friday Puzzler at <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fray.camdenfamily.com%3Anr8Wfzs5RNhu5OZT_80z8UhvscU&amp;cuid=3321886" rel="nofollow noopener" title="http://ray.camdenfamily.com">http://ray.camdenfamily.com</a><br>Description: Takes either raw HTML or a URL and processes the HTML and returns the contents of HTML comments.<br>---&gt;</p><p>&lt;cfparam name="form.userInput" default=""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.resultTitle = "&lt;em&gt;No comments to display&lt;/em&gt;"&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.checkUserInput = ""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.rawHtml = ""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.thisUrl = ""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.httpResult = ""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.thisComment = ""&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.finalResult = ArrayNew(1)&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.startingPos = 1&gt;<br>&lt;cfset variables.processForComments = 1&gt;</p><p>&lt;cfif len(form.userInput)&gt;<br>	&lt;!--- Look for a URL ---&gt;<br>	&lt;cfset checkUserInput = REFindNoCase("\b(http\:\/\/\S+)\b", form.userInput, 1, true)&gt;</p><p>	&lt;!--- If it was a URL, get the content of the HTML page ---&gt;<br>	&lt;cfif checkUserInput.len[1]&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset thisUrl = Mid(form.userInput, checkUserInput.pos[1], checkUserInput.len[1])&gt;<br>		&lt;cfhttp url="#thisUrl#" method="get" result="httpResult"&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset rawHtml = httpResult.fileContent&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset resultTitle = "Comments found at " &amp; thisURL&gt;<br>	&lt;cfelse&gt;<br>		&lt;!--- otherwise, let's process the user input directly ---&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset rawHtml = form.userInput&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset resultTitle = "Comments submitted in the form below"&gt;<br>	&lt;/cfif&gt;</p><p>	&lt;cfloop condition="processForComments eq 1"&gt;<br>		&lt;!--- This comment regex found at: <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fostermiller.org%2Ffindhtmlcomment.html%3AGAdu-YRpxP-KN8kHh5ro6djkSIM&amp;cuid=3321886" rel="nofollow noopener" title="http://ostermiller.org/findhtmlcomment.html">http://ostermiller.org/find...</a> ---&gt;<br>		&lt;cfset thisComment = REFindNoCase("\&lt;![ \r\n\t]*(--([^\-]|[\r\n]|-[^\-])*--[ \r\n\t]*)\&gt;", rawHtml, startingPos, true)&gt;<br>		&lt;cfif thisComment.pos[1]&gt;<br>			&lt;!--- Grab the contents of the HTML comment ---&gt;<br>			&lt;cfset ArrayAppend(finalResult, mid(rawHtml, (thisComment.pos[1] + 4), (thisComment.len[1] - 7)))&gt;<br>			&lt;!--- Move the starting position up, so that we don't grab this comment again ---&gt;<br>			&lt;cfset startingPos = thisComment.pos[1] + thisComment.len[1]&gt;<br>		&lt;cfelse&gt;<br>			&lt;!--- No more comments found, stop looping ---&gt;<br>			&lt;cfset processForComments = 0&gt;<br>		&lt;/cfif&gt;<br>	&lt;/cfloop&gt;<br>&lt;/cfif&gt;</p><p>&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "<a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2FTR%2Fxhtml1%2FDTD%2Fxhtml1-transitional.dtd%3AlsD79NC9EpzB4LCkih033Se6Csw&amp;cuid=3321886" rel="nofollow noopener" title="http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1...</a>"&gt;<br>&lt;html xmlns="<a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1999%2Fxhtml%3AA6NInarpbzWm6HKZDXlFrwZefzc&amp;cuid=3321886" rel="nofollow noopener" title="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml</a>"&gt;<br>&lt;head&gt;<br>&lt;meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1" /&gt;<br>&lt;title&gt;Check HTML for Comments&lt;/title&gt;<br>&lt;/head&gt;</p><p>&lt;body&gt;<br>&lt;cfoutput&gt;<br>	&lt;p&gt;#resultTitle#&lt;/p&gt;</p><p>&lt;cfif arraylen(variables.finalResult)&gt;<br>	&lt;cfdump var="#variables.finalResult#"&gt;<br>&lt;/cfif&gt;</p><p>&lt;hr /&gt;<br>&lt;form action="#CGI.SCRIPT_NAME#" method="post"&gt;<br>	Enter URL or HTML Code Here:&lt;